Sensei Piet van Rensburg with sensei William Malebana of JKA Pietersburg Karate Club who, under the watchful eye of South African JKA Chief Instructor Johan le Grange, graded to third Dan in Johannesburg. Malebana has been participating in karate for 23 years and, according to Van Rensburg, is a dedicated and hard-working karateka who deserves this achievement. (Photo: Supplied)